{"tid":2277380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登最新演說再稱 :「全美2.3億人」死於武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-11-08T12:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T12:18:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6ebdf2722bdca56bd802b506eb4204cbe28148","tid":2277380,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F2ibtLlhyOuv1AdFJQmL_A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMzNy4xNTYxNzcxNTYxNzcxNA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Vl13JfSMfYkUyQi3H46j4g--~B/aD00NTI7dz04NTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/ctwant_com_582/7769416e2ae75e1524270693fdfa1275\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FF2ibtLlhyOuv1AdFJQmL_A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTMzNy4xNTYxNzcxNTYxNzcxNA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVl13JfSMfYkUyQi3H46j4g--~B%2FaD00NTI7dz04NTg7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fctwant_com_582%2F7769416e2ae75e1524270693fdfa1275&h=e5972001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020美國總統大選歷經數天激烈拉鋸後，終於在美國時間7日結果出爐，由民主黨候選人拜登（Joe Biden）奪得寶座，以290票選舉人票打敗現任總統川普（Donald Trump），當選第46任美國總統，沒想到晚間拜登在發表勝選演說時，竟口誤稱全美有2.3億人都死於新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，回顧拜登在競選期間，三番兩次爆出失言情況，讓他一度被川普揶揄「痴呆」，沒想到今晚拜登現身德拉瓦州威名頓市（Wilmington）發表演說時，竟然又再度口誤，他表示「我希望能帶給今年因可怕病毒而失去摯愛的2.3億&hellip;23萬多個家庭帶來一些安慰與慰藉。」<br />\n<br />\n儘管拜登立刻改口更正，但依舊被多家媒體大作文章，而這並非他首次在講述疫情數據時出錯，其實早在9月20日，拜登在費城演說時，便曾指「新冠肺炎造成2億人死亡」，但他當下並沒有發現口誤。根據美國約翰霍普金斯大學疫情統計，目前全美累積有986萬人染疫，23萬7113人病逝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/拜登又口誤-勝選演說稱-全美2-3億人-死於新冠肺炎-114113740.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%8F%88%E5%8F%A3%E8%AA%A4-%E5%8B%9D%E9%81%B8%E6%BC%94%E8%AA%AA%E7%A8%B1-%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E2-3%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA-%E6%AD%BB%E6%96%BC%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-114113740.html&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq74TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=96df5a2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/拜登又口誤-勝選演說稱-全美2-3億人-死於新冠肺炎-114113740.html</a>"},{"pid":"10524a578ae29d9af54b013b65b2e446af4ed0ab","tid":2277380,"uid":59357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:17:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24e16eaf68e9c22d1c98f21905ed580855763a6f","tid":2277380,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}